Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:19.36,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:21.87,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.68,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:31.43,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:36.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.80,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:51.75,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:57.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:01.57,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:02.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:07.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:13.83,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.38,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:23.14,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.88,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.64,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.80,0:00:05.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.98,0:00:10.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.68,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.94,0:00:31.43,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.03,0:00:36.92,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.80,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.99,0:00:46.61,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.61,0:00:51.75,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.87,0:00:57.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.00,0:01:01.57,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.95,0:01:07.20,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.20,0:01:13.83,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.38,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!

Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:27.39,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見渡す世界 足はすくむけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:31.26,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}歩みを止めぬビリーバー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.93,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幾度の傷 痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:41.16,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一筋の強気染み付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:46.01,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}戸惑いに揺れる心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:50.95,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}足取りは覚束なくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:53.55,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}恐れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:59.16,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}希望へと両手伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.47,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}通り抜ける 願い纏う風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:09.69,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷わない瞳はただ前を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:15.16,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}共に行けば 絶望など他愛ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:20.22,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重い闇さえ 振り払うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.76,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸を狂わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:27.01,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未來を力で
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.12,0:22:27.39,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}放眼整个世界 即便双脚在颤抖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.25,0:22:31.26,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸怀信念之人也不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.93,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无数次受伤 无数次疼痛中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.93,0:22:41.16,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}被那一身骨气所振奋
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.24,0:22:46.01,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷惑中动摇的心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.44,0:22:50.95,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便步履已經蹒跚
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.31,0:22:53.55,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}也绝不畏惧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.88,0:22:59.16,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}向着希望 努力伸出双手
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.73,0:23:04.47,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}清风吹过 带来一份祈愿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.57,0:23:09.69,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}坚定不移的瞳孔 只看前路
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.12,0:23:15.16,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}与你同行 绝望又算得上什么
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.32,0:23:20.22,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}再沉重的黑暗 也能一挥而散
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.76,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}挑逗着心跳节拍
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.76,0:23:27.01,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未來 由我掌握
